            "heading": "Material & Fabric",
            "icon": "leather",
            "content": "<p><strong>Premium Quality Materials</strong></p><p><strong>Fabric Composition:</strong></p><ul><li>Main Fabric: 100% Premium Cotton</li><li>Lining: Soft Cotton Blend</li></ul><p><strong>Why Premium Cotton?</strong></p><p>Our premium cotton is carefully selected for its softness, breathability, and durability—perfect for your child's delicate skin. It's gentle, hypoallergenic, and maintains its quality wash after wash.</p><p><strong>Care Instructions:</strong></p><ul><li>Machine wash cold with similar colors</li><li>Use gentle cycle for longevity</li><li>Do not bleach</li><li>Tumble dry low or hang to dry</li><li>Iron on low heat if needed</li></ul><p><strong>Durability & Comfort:</strong></p><p>Our premium cotton blends are designed to withstand active play while keeping your little one comfortable all day long. The soft lining ensures maximum comfort against sensitive skin.</p>{{ block.settings.page.content }}{{ product.metafields.custom.material_rich | metafield_tag }}",
